<title>JAPAN: Ishihara Construction 96/97 loss due to loans.</title>
<headline>Ishihara Construction 96/97 loss due to loans.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-04-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Ishihara Construction Co Ltd said on Wednesday that it expects to have posted a net loss of 10.85 billion yen in 1996/97 due mostly to a loss from guaranteed loans and an increase in its loan loss reserve.</p>
<p>The company said in a statement that it posted a loss of 6.35 billion yen from loan guarantees it extended to its group companies.</p>
<p>It also put up a loan loss reserve of 4.07 billion yen in the last business year.</p>
